---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { config } from "../config";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms and conditions for using Votting Group products and services.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="reveal mb-12">
        <span class="text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[var(--color-accent)] mb-4 block">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Last updated: March 18, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 space-y-8 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-[15px]">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using the {config.legalName} ("{config.companyName}") website and products, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
            If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">2. Products and Services</h2>
          <p>{config.legalName} provides digital products and services including but not limited to:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
            {["REST APIs and data services", "Automation workflow packages", "Digital templates and documents", "AI-powered tools and skills", "Web applications and SaaS tools", "Custom development and consulting services"].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
                <span>{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">3. Purchases and Payments</h2>
          <p>
            Payments are processed through third-party providers including Stripe, Gumroad, RapidAPI, Etsy, and Fiverr.
            Each platform's terms and refund policies apply in addition to these terms.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            All prices are listed in the currency specified on the respective platform. Prices may change without prior notice,
            but changes will not affect existing orders.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">4. Digital Product Licence</h2>
          <p>
            When you purchase a digital product (template, workflow pack, skill, or tool), you receive a
            <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable licence</strong> to use the product
            for your own personal or business purposes. You may not:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
            {["Redistribute, resell, or share the product with third parties", "Claim the product as your own original creation", "Use the product in a way that directly competes with Votting Group", "Reverse-engineer or attempt to extract source code from compiled products"].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
                <span>{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">5. API Usage</h2>
          <p>
            API access is subject to rate limits and fair use policies as defined on the respective platform (e.g., RapidAPI).
            Abuse, excessive requests, scraping, or attempts to circumvent rate limits may result in access being suspended or revoked without refund.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">6. Refund Policy</h2>
          <p>Due to the digital nature of our products:</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Digital downloads:</strong> No refunds after delivery, unless the product is materially defective or not as described.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">API subscriptions:</strong> Cancellable at any time through the platform. Refunds per platform policy.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
              <span><strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Custom services:</strong> Refund terms defined per individual project agreement.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            If you believe a product is defective, contact us at <a href={`mailto:${config.email}`} class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">{config.email}</a> within 14 days of purchase.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content, code, designs, and branding on this website and in our products are the intellectual property of {config.legalName}
            unless otherwise stated. Open-source components are used under their respective licences.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            {config.legalName} provides products and services "as is" without warranty of any kind, express or implied.
            To the maximum extent permitted by law, we shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages
            arising from the use of our products or services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Republic of Estonia.
            Any disputes arising from these terms shall be resolved in the courts of Tallinn, Estonia.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">10. Severability</h2>
          <p>
            If any provision of these terms is found to be unenforceable or invalid, that provision shall be limited or
            eliminated to the minimum extent necessary, and the remaining provisions shall remain in full force and effect.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">11. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to update these terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
            Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <div class="hr-gradient mb-8"></div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions about these terms:</p>
          <div class="mt-3 p-5 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-bg-secondary)] border border-[var(--color-border)] text-sm">
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)] font-medium">{config.legalName}</p>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-1">{config.location}</p>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
              <a href={`mailto:${config.email}`} class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">{config.email}</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
